{"tid":718017,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術］香港嘅醫療制度存在gender bias嗎","createTime":"2018-06-26T12:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T04:04:33.000Z","uid":145588,"like":131,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"75104851a5db74cf2000edf69f0da8676ed9cc33","tid":718017,"uid":145588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:57:22.000Z","msg":"個人認為係有嘅。一直都覺得香港嘅醫療制度落後於其他先進國家，而gender bias問題便是一例。<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<br />\n1. 女護士可以進出男女病房，但男護只係限於男病房。<br />\n<br />\n2. 男護唔可以assist對於女病人嘅治療。<br />\n<br />\n3. 男性不能夠成為助產士。（講緊40年前因著1976 年嘅Sex Discrimination Act 所以UK已經allow咗male midwives 呢樣嘢）<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解嗰啲婦科唔ban埋男醫生，只係唔俾male nurses/ male midwives做？因為啲女病人鍾意赤裸下身對住男醫生咩？選擇性gender bias?<br />\n唔好同我講咩男醫生體貼啲手勢好啲乜乜柒柒，我夠可以話男護男助產士手勢好啲啦，咁又唔allow人地去做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw pts 1,2喺外國e.g. UK/US已經唔係問題，真係唔明點解香港哩啲已發展城市嘅醫療制度咁落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有一堆醫療事故但涉事醫護人員不負責任更不在話下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港醫療制度存在gender bias<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主鳩up 香港醫療制度不存在gender bias<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：絲打，唔洗人身攻擊話我葡萄定點。只係見女權崛起爭取女性權益，但對於男性嘅不公社會卻視而不見先想討論下。純學術討論，No offence <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c4f43bc541b53f71dff930b71291d0ebad2a96","tid":718017,"uid":105715,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"5. 女護士喺香港係被稱呼做姑娘，而男護士則被稱呼做男姑娘"},{"pid":"7985192239f57b91f0d5786b65c81ffe12b35f56","tid":718017,"uid":30708,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26